records.addlTxt: Plea/sentencing hearing on November 8, 2022 at 03:30 pm.
Bail/bond hearing on November 8, 2022 at 03:30 pm.

1:04 PM/ RM 203.  Defendant Jessica A. Walton appeared by video, in custody in Langlade County Jail. Attorney Elizabeth R. Gebert in court for State of Wisconsin, via zoom. Court reviews case history. Def. has filed waiver of attorney form. Court questions if Def. continues to wish to represent self. Def. confirms. Court reviews waiver of attorney form with Def. and Def. constitutional rights. Court finds Def. is competent to represent self and is entering freely and voluntarily and will allow Def. to proceed and represent self. State questions if Def. would like to waive time limits for P.H. Court questions if Def. would like to have a P.H. within time limits or waive time limits. Def. would like to waive P.H. completely. Court finds waiver of P.H. is entered freely and voluntarily and finds probable cause. State is ready to proceed with arraignment today and notes information to be filed mirrors criminal complaint and can send a copy over to Def. Def. is okay to proceed with arraignment today. Court questions if State would like Def. to plea. State confirms. Def. enters Not Guilty plea on Ct. 1, Ct. 2 and Ct. 3. Court enters Not Guilty plea on all counts. State requests Status Conference and notes a copy of the information and an offer will be sent to the Def. today. Bond continues.
Status conference scheduled for November 21, 2022 at 11:00 am.

11:15 AM/ RM 203.  Defendant Jessica A. Walton appeared by video, in custody in Langlade County Jail.  Attorney Elizabeth R. Gebert in court for State of Wisconsin, via zoom. Court reviews case history. Case was to be called on 10/24, but was rescheduled for today as Court was overbooked. Court notes appointment of counsel report. Def. would like to represent self. Court orders Def. to complete waiver of attorney form. 
Hearing scheduled for October 26, 2022 at 01:00 pm.

3:31 PM/RM 301. Defendant Jessica A. Walton appeared by video, in custody in Langlade County Jail.  Attorney Kelly Hays in court for State of Wisconsin, via zoom. Court reviews case history. Adjourned initial appearance scheduled for October 24, 2022 at 01:30 pm.

1:01 PM/Rm. 301. Defendant Jessica A. Walton appeared by video, in custody in Langlade County Jail.  Attorney Elizabeth R. Gebert in court for State of Wisconsin, via zoom. Def. has copy of complaint, advised of charges and penalties. Def. given Atty rights and given 4 options, PD, hire own or court appointed Atty or represent self.
